Title: use sentence case for local check metric labels
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1654849424
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.2.0b1

Since werk 12185 we automatically show metrics in the output of local checks.
The metric names are now consistently converted to sentence case.
Below are examples for the automatic conversion

<tt>LONG_METRIC_NAME</tt> -> <i>Long metric name</i>

<tt>recommendation4WHO</tt> -> <i>Recommendation 4 WHO</i>

<tt>weekIncidence</tt> -> <i>Week incidence</i>

<tt>zombie_apocalypse</tt> -> <i>Zombie apocalypse</i>

